\c 3
\s Hamani anoronga kuparadza VaJudha
\p
\v 1 Shure kwezvinhu izvi mambo Ahasuwerusi wakakwiridzira Hamani mwanakomana waHamedhata\x + 5.11. 10.2.\x* muAgagi\x + 3.10. 8.3,5. 9.24. Num.. 24.7. 1 Sam. 15.8.\x*, ndokumusimudzira, ndokuisa chigaro chake pamusoro pemachinda ese aiva naye\x + 5.11. 10.2.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino varanda vese vamambo vaiva pasuwo ramambo vakakotama ndokufugamira Hamani; nokuti mambo waiva araira saizvozvo maererano naye. Asi Modhekai haana kukotama kana kufugama\x + 2.19.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino varanda vamambo vaiva pasuwo ramambo\x + 2.19.\x* vakati kuna Modhekai: Unodarikirei murairo wamambo\x + 3.2.\x*?
\v 4 Zvino zvakaitika pavaitaura zuva nezuva kwaari, kuti haana kuteerera kwavari, zvekuti vakaudza Hamani kuti vaone kuti mashoko aModhekai angamira here; nokuti waiva avaudza kuti muJudha.
\v 5 Hamani paakaona kuti Modhekai haakotami kana kumufugamira\x + 3.2. 5.9.\x*, Hamani ndokuzara nekutsamwa\x + Dhan. 3.19.\x*.
\v 6 Asi wakashora pameso ake kuisa ruoko kuna Modhekai oga, nokuti vaiva vamuzivisa rudzi rwaModhekai; naizvozvo Hamani wakatsvaka kuparadza VaJudha vese vaiva paushe hwese hwaAhasuwerusi, rudzi rwaModhekai.
\p
\v 7 Mumwedzi wekutanga, ndiwo mwedzi waNisani\x + Neh. 2.1.\x*, mugore regumi nemaviri ramambo Ahasuwerusi, vakakanda Puri\x + 9.24,26.\x*, ndiwo mujenya, pamberi paHamani kubva pazuva kusvika pazuva uye kubva pamwedzi kusvika pamwedzi wegumi nemiviri\x + Vato. 20.9.\x*, ndiwo mwedzi waAdhari\x + Ezi. 6.15.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Zvino Hamani wakati kuna mambo Ahasuwerusi: Kune rumwe rudzi, rwakapararira nekutekeshera pakati pevanhu kumatunhu ese eumambo hwenyu; uye mirairo yavo\x + Ezi. 4.12,13. Mab. 16.20,21.\x* yakasiyana neyevanhu vese\x + 1.7.\x*, uye mirairo yamambo havasi kuita; zvino kuna mambo hazvibatsiri kuvarega.
\v 9 Kana zvakanaka kuna mambo, ngakunyorwe kuti vaparadzwe; uye ndichayerera matarenda* zvuru gumi esirivha mumaoko evaiti vebasa, kuisa mune zvakakosha zvamambo.
\v 10 Zvino mambo wakabvisa chindori chake paruoko rwake, ndokuchipa kuna Hamani mwanakomana waHamedhata\x + 8.2. 3.12. 8.8,10. Gen.. 41.42.\x* muAgagi\x + 3.10. 8.3,5. 9.24. Num.. 24.7. 1 Sam. 15.8.\x*, muvengi weVaJudha.
\v 11 Zvino mambo wakati kuna Hamani: Sirivha yakapiwa kwauri, nevanhu, kuita navo sezvakanaka pameso ako.
\v 12 Zvino kwakadanwa vanyori vamambo\x + 8.9.\x* mumwedzi wekutanga pazuva regumi nematatu rawo\x + 3.7.\x*; zvino kwakanyorwa zvichienderana nezvese Hamani zvaaiva araira kumachinda amambo\x + Ezi. 8.36.\x*, nekuvatongi vaiva pamusoro pedunhu nedunhu\x + 1 Madz. 10.15.\x*, nekumisoro yerudzi nerudzi; dunhu nedunhu zvichienderana nechinyorwa chavo\x + 1.22. 8.9.\x* uye rudzi nerudzi zvichienderana nemutauro wavo; dzakanyorwa muzita ramambo Ahasuwerusi\x + 8.8,10. 1 Madz. 21.8.\x*, ndokudhindwa nechindori chamambo.
\v 13 Zvino tsamba dzakatumwa neruoko rwevamhanyi\x + 8.10. 2 Makor. 30.6.\x* kumatunhu ese amambo, kuparadza, kuuraya, nekutsakatisa VaJudha vese, kubva kune wechidiki kusvika kune wakwegura, vanana nevanhukadzi\x + 7.4.\x*, pazuva rimwe\x + 8.12. 9.1.\x*, neregumi nematatu remwedzi wegumi nemiviri, uri mwedzi weAdhari\x + Ezi. 6.15.\x*, uye zvakatapiwa zvavo zvipambwe\x + 8.11.\x*.
\v 14 Chikoponorwa chechinyorwa chekuti murairo upiwe kudunhu rimwe nerimwe, chikava pachena kuvanhu vese kuti vagadzirire zuva iro\x + 8.13,14.\x*.
\v 15 Vamhanyi vakabuda, vakakurumidza neshoko ramambo\x + 8.10. 2 Makor. 30.6.\x*; mutemo ndokupiwa paShushani muzinda; mambo naHamani ndokugara kunwa, asi guta reShushani rakadziyaniswa\x + 8.15. Eki. 14.3.\x*.